                        <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-818-18600917 t18600917-818-punishment-76"></join>Three Years' Penal Servitude.</rs>
                  </hi>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Before Robert Malcolm Kerr, Esq.</hi>
